&lt;li&gt;All of our hardware is fully owned by DediCube LLC. No leases, no rentals, no reselling!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Chinese language sales and technical support translation assistance! (&lt;b&gt;我们已有中文销售代表为您服务! 中文技术支持将在不久后推出!&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
